    "body": "This PR makes bitcoin core changes needed to be compatible with https://github.com/bitcoin-core/libmultiprocess/pull/231, which adds windows to support libmultiprocess.\r\n\r\nThe two PRs are meant to be reviewed in parallel and there is a draft PR https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/32387 combining both of these with more changes to enable IPC by default on windows.",
